content: Best HP 12C calculator in the market. Very satisfied user for years.

Great app. I use it daily in my finance profession. Does functions I can't do in MS EXCEL, including complex cash flow and IRR analysis. I have owned this for perhaps ten years, after having used the original HP 12C for over twenty years (which I still own). No negatives. Works like it is supposed to, very fast, accurate, never crashes, no ads, minimal permissions. Also good response from developer with help in porting app to new phone.

Works well. Highly unfair to have to pay for this on a new phone when I've already paid once for it.

Works exactly like the original HP calculators. Only it's much, much faster. I've now used it for several years. I routinely run programs on it to run net worth etc. The programs run considerably faster than on the HP12C Platinum. Help file is an excellent reminder if you need to jog your memory. Also.I forgot to mention that it has a fantastic scientific calculator as well.
Ed Falk did a great job.
Great hp calculator
Seems to 'work' on my Pixel 4 under os10 but the landlords advise it's out of date and request you hassle the dev about it.?
Does not work... no documentation...I want my money back
Best HP-12c app out there. Highly recommended.
Great app to have - recommended to my students in college. Newer graphics but still very functional....short learning curve.
Great app

For those of you who've always wanted an HP-12C calculator but not wanted to spend $$$, this calculator is for you. Very powerful and easy to use...even includes scientific and regular calculations. Well worth the price.

I have used other apps and this one by far without question is amazingly the Best overall one that is available. The updates have improved as well. RPN does appear to be confusing and awkward and might seem like it would be easier to stay with the others and what you have been taught. If you truly want to learn anything you have to take an interest in it study it and use it to understand it. Therefore do so with Faulk's RpnCalc Financial Calculator upgrade and you will come to love it as I do!

Best RPN app out there. You have the choice of 3 layouts - basic (really basic), scientific, and of course financial. I've been using this app for years. I recently switched phones, and had difficulties getting the app working on the new phone (forgot to update my last beta version with the  free upgrade code). Contacted the developer and receive a free coupon for the most recent version. What more could you wish for from an app and a developer.
used for many years, outstanding!
Best option on the market

Little pissed I had to rebuy the app. I used the other version for years though and figured it was only right to kick the dev some more cash because the app is great and even paying twice it is still better than buying the hp12c version. Not going to lie, if it happens again, I'll simply grab the apk from a more nefarious source. If you're going to change apps like that give old users an upgrade path. Thanks for making a great product.
Just like my HP 12-C, which is the best calculator I have owned.

If you use or have used a 12C calculator, this will be instantly familiar. It's fast, accurate, & actually has more functions than the old 12C. The developer responded quickly when I had trouble with getting updates, and solved the problem for me. Only wish is for a more easily readable display. Larger or heavier font for both the keys and the display would be helpful for those of us with aging vision. Otherwise, it's a great app, and one that I use daily.
Best RPN Financial calculator for Android I've found. I've tried all I could find.

What a great discovery. The definitive RPN calculator with 12C functions. It also has the bonus of a few very carefully thought out additions that are a natural extension to the power of the 12C in an Android environment. Also nice non- financial functions as well.
Great clone of the HP 12C. More bang for your bucks than the original HP app that cost twice as much. Saved me numerous times.

I am in the commercial real estate industry and have been using hp12c calculators since the 1980s. When I'm away from my desk I rely on the Edward Falk version that is installed on my phone. It looks and responds identically to my 3 physical hp12s. I can't thank Mr. Falk enough!
Don't really need the financial version, but they don't take money for RPNCalc so I had to buy *something*.

Like all others, I have used the original 12C since the beginning of time (hands down the best financial calculator the world has ever seen). But I have also surrendered to this convenient, close-to-perfect replica (and more üôÇ) never-fails you piece of technology-in-your-hands. It comes supremely recommended.
The best balance between modern and classic.

This is an outstanding app that I have used nearly every day since 2011.  It was quite beneficial when I first started to use it, and it has been improved over the years. The developer has responded quickly and effectively to requests and suggestions.The functionality is now richer than the iconoclastic device on which it is modeled, and with modern processors it also calculates much faster.  This app allow me to carry one fewer device and brings an end to frequent battery replacement on the calculator. I can also use it under low light conditions. If you use financial calculations and enjoy the RPN entry method, this is a true no-brainer. I give RpnCalc Financial Calculator my highest recommendation. .

Absolutely love this calculator app.  My favorite calculator has always been my embarrassingly old HP 12C, so it's wonderful to have an app that functions like it with the benefit of not having to deal with distracting ads for a reasonable price.  I love that I can lock it into portrait layout so I don't have to turn my phone to use.  The aesthetics are perfect.  It's wonderful to have its functionality in the convenience of my phone, which I always have handy, instead of having to make the choice of using a crappy calculator app or getting up to track down my HP 12C.  LOVE IT!

Fully compatible with the HP 12c and with useful features the calculator lacks (e. g., tape, amort table). And it is easy to switch this app to scientific calculator mode should you need trigonometric functions.
Really great app. Great customer support. All the financial calculator I'll ever need!

Your app is fantastic! It save a me from carrying multiple devices! I still like to use the physical 12C when I‚Äôm at the office‚Ä¶something about the feel of the keys!  This is one of the first apps I purchased when I got a smartphone. It has been invaluable to me in my business, especially since the physical calculator I have is over 30 years old!

TMV calculations are off compared to Excel and HP12C . As an illustration,  try it yourself and enter these numbers: $100000 (FV), 9% (i), 5 (n),  calculate PV. Off by 6%? Is there a setting to make calculations more  precise?  Revised review: 15 August 2018. Now the calculation result is the same between HP12C and the android app. Thanks for the corrections
replyContent: Hi Budana; I just tried your example myself and got the same result to as many decimal places as the calculator will display: -64,993.13863. Please contact me off line at falk@efalk.org and we'll try to figure out what was different.

content:
Falk did a great job. Prefer it over the others. Once you understand RPN 
you will see its value. More memory.

I started using the HP12C in 1984 and this replicates it perfectly. It's a 
joy to use, look no farther and download it.
Best HP12c template I've used. Awesome calculator

The calculator is great but I resent having to pay a second time as the 
financial features have been removed from my original copy when I had to 
reload it. Emailed the developer and got no response.
replyContent: Hi Henry; please try me again at falk@efalk.org. I searched my email and didn't see anything from you, so I suspect it got lost. If you paid twice, I'll give a refund. If not, I'll help you get the app back into your device.

content: Great app. It works just like the HP 12C plus it has features that the HP doesn't have.
I have used the HP12C since 1982 & this app is almost the same, but better since it has better features & is faster!

I have been RPN-ing since 1976 (yuk)! Been on an actual HP12C since they were launched... And then Ed Falk launched this  -  as the description says "The best financial calculator on the market." Period....
Better than original. Also has full amort table from landscape mode.
Every bit as good as my trusty 12C.
Awesome RPN calculator. Been using for 7 years.
Just perfect

For those of us who know that RPN is the only notation that reflects the way that we humans actually experience mathematical thought, and who remember RPN financial calculators fondly, this particular calculator app is the *only*. one worth considering.
The HP 12c was all you needed for a good estimate of complex financial products. This is even better. And you can amaze your office mates by using reverse Polish notation !
Fantastic app! Works perfectly like my college calculators I still have, which are as old as my wife.  Highly recommend!
Used the HP-12c through college and in finance since then and love it. Now I can leave the 12c at home and still have the features on my phone. Well done, Ed and thank you.

I found this app many years ago and it has accompanied each new cell phone purchase I have made.  It's emulation of an HP 12C has made it indispensable in my line of work as I no longer need to carry a separate financial calculator with me.  Add to that tremendous support from the developer!

Unreserved appreciation and praise.   The only negative review is someone who cannot make his phone work.  I own and have used a HP-12C since 1976. I wonder what could be on HP's mind that they don't want to let Falk call this an HP-12C emulator -- It is an improved and modern 12C. Its existence and widespread use can only add to the considerable stature of the original.

I've been using a financial RPN calculator for about 15 years. They are, to me, so much simpler and logical to operate. This one on the Play Store is the best one available. It is fast, accurate and easily displays in either portrait or landscape mode. It is worth every penny charged. The author is solid and doesn't update just for the sake of updating.
Great app for doing TValue calculations, calculate amortization, loan payments, etc. I have used this for years and it is a must have!
I love this app!

I have been using a version of this app for years. I love having a full RPN Financial calculator with me all the time. It's even better than my HP 12C because it has a larger stack and it's always visible on the scree. It makes longer calculations so much easier when you can see the stack right there. And the few times that I've needed support, the developer has been extremely quick to respond and help out. I highly recommend this app.
If you need what a 12C does, buy this app and skip all the free ones. Don't over think it or waste your time. Buy the app and go to work. I've not found anything a "real" 12C will do that it won't.

Dear Mr Falk,   Thank you for your help in recovering the RpnCalc Financial app that I had previously purchased. It's a tremendous app and better than the HP12C calculator itself! May you have continued success in the work you are doing. And again, thank you your support. If I could give more than 5 stars I would! Have a blessed day!            Sincerely,         Aaron Bradford
Excellent app - best of the best! I've  used it and its predecessor version for many years and never had a problem. Highly recommended.
Best financial calculator for Android!
Excellent app - exactly like a HP12C, but faster and without the limitations.

This is an excellent application, and the support is fantastic!  As a bit of a calculator junkie (I even have one the the original Casio graphing calculator from the 80s), I have an affinity for them for whatever reason and this one is top notch.  Plus, the developer helped me get through some issues with the Google Play Store and I am a very happy camper!
I have an original calculator on which this (may?) be modeled... This one from E Falk  has 21st century features.
Great app, awesome developer!! Have used this app for many years. Best app of its kind!

I have been using this App for over a decade and have been using the HP-12C at my desk since that calculator first came out over 30 years ago.  I no longer have to worry about leaving the physical HP-12C behind when I leave my office because the Falk RpnCalc Financial Calculator works just as well and takes no more room than my cell phone which I am carrying anyway.  Thanks for making a great App and for supporting it through the years.
Best calc on the market.

I have been using this app for years. As a Financial Advisor, I use it for on-the-fly calculations in client appointments all the time. In college I used an HP12-C and since then this has been my replacement. A must have for any financial professional.
Love this App.  To me, it 100 times better than my old HP 12C. If you own a HP 12C, you owe it to yourself to get this plus you won't have carry around another tiny machine.  It's "AWESOME" !!!   :-)
UPDATE:   This is a great app.  Can't live without it.
Best financial calculator app available.  For only $4.99 you get exactly the same features as any financial calculator with the convenience of it being on your phone.
A quality calculator! Perfect for financial and other calculations

I have a HP12c that I have used for years but I purchased this app a couple of years ago and haven't used the 12c since?this just feels better. Developer has done a great job was really helpful in getting app into my new phone
Long time user of this Rpn calculator and love it. Closest thing to a HP 12c in the play store.
The only calculator I use. Highly recommended the publisher is a great guy too
Awesome!
If you prefer RPN then this is the best financial calculator on the market
Excellent calculator.  Just like my HP12c.  Don't use it very often but very useful to have around when I do.
This is the best financial calculator in the Play Store.  It has all the functionality of the 12C and then some.

This is a great reliable app!  The developer also provides excellent customer support based on recent experience.  I really enjoy having the HP Business calculator interface on my smartphone.  It's truly the best of both worlds on a single device.

This developer is top notch. I have used this rpn financial calculator daily for years, relying on it for bond calculations and time value of money calculations. After email and text, it's my most used app. Highly recommended. Great app.
Accurate,and excellent UI.

I've been using this application for many years, probably since first became available, 8, 9, 10 years maybe.  I've consistently found this to be the best financial reverse polish notation calculator on the market, this includes the HP12C; and recommend it highly, five stars, and would give six if I could :)
I'm a long time HP RPN calculator fan. This is the best RPN calc out there.
This is a great application. I have been using it for a long time.
I use this app as much or more than any on my device.  Much better than the HP version I have on my iPad.
for preserving the techniques, algorithms & habits you may have formed while using a popular handheld financial calculator. This turns my Pixel XL into that old friend every time I launch the app.
Superb app. Highly recommended. Sorry for the hoops HP made you jump through.
